Design a Web page to display the sum of even numbers between 1 to 20.

Display heading using H1 tag.

Write a javascript function which should calculate the sum and display the result in a div tag with id “result”

Web Page snapshot for your reference-----------------------------------------------------

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Even Sum</title>
    </head>
    <body onload="evensum()">
        <h1>Display Even Number & Sum</h1>
        <div id="result"></div>
        <script>
            function evensum(){
                var c=0,sum=0;
              while(c<=20){
                  sum=sum+c;
                  c=c+2;
                }
                 document.getElementById('result').innerHTML='Total:'+sum;
            }
         </script>
    </body>
</html>
